1.title: Episode #1.1
1.plot: A ten-part intimate series profiling a key member of the Brasil team with each episode. With exclusive footage, interviews and exciting career highlights ?Stars Of Brasil? reveals the personal story behind some of the world?s best players. Featuring - Neymar, Oscar, Thiago Silva, David Luiz, Paulinho, Ramires, Lucas Moura, Luiz Gustavo and Willian.
